  endingTitle: 'Bad Ending: Exposed!'
  endingText: "You\u2019ve been talking nonsense the whole time! Now they are extremely
    furious. One lashes out with their upper limbs, the other drives a kick straight
    into you, and suddenly everyone\u2019s moving at once as you\u2019re dragged
    off mid-chaos. Cooperation? War? Not like you\u2019re in any position to worry
    about it."
